BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Labels and a marker let you date containers so you know freshness.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (You do not need expensive equipment. Start with containers and a good knife.) Tj ET
