q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Always shop with a list based on your weekly meal plan.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Check store flyers and apps for sales before making your list.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Buy proteins in bulk when on sale and freeze what you will not use immediately.) Tj ET
