BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Buy store brand staples like rice, beans, oats, and canned goods.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Frozen vegetables are nutritious, affordable, and last much longer.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Avoid shopping when hungry as this leads to impulse purchases.) Tj ET
